 The first son of Nigeria’s famous actor, Yul Edochie, has been reported dead on Thursday morning. Yul had on January 4 celebrated the 16th birthday of his son, Kambilichukwu Edochie via his verified Instagram handle  Meanwhile, confirming the news of his death, a family member who spoke with Vanguard, was quoted as saying that Kambilichukwu died on Thursday. “After his exam in school, he joined his mates to play football and he developed a seizure and was rushed to the Mother and Child Hospital. All efforts by the doctors to resuscitate him proved abortive,” she added.